ware", "bbox": [162.5, 907.5, 1087.5, 928.4]}, {"text": "development costs that had been capitalized in accordance with ASC 985-20 of $19.4 million, $25.6 million and", "bbox": [162.5, 932.5, 1100.7, 953.4]}, {"text": "$12.7 million as of December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015, respectively. Leased equipment includes amounts held", "bbox": [162.5, 957.5, 1089.5, 978.4]}, {"text": "under capital leases for automobiles, computer software and computer equipment.", "bbox": [162.5, 982.5, 847.0, 1003.4]}, {"text": "8.", "bbox": [162.5, 1040.1, 178.1, 1061.0]}, {"text": "Acquisitions", "bbox": [199.0, 1040.1, 308.9, 1061.0]}, {"text": "2017 Acquisitions", "bbox": [183.3, 1076.3, 335.5, 1097.1]}, {"text": "On December 29, 2017, the Company acquired 100 percent of the stock of PowerAdvocate, Inc.", "bbox": [225.0, 1112.2, 1027.7, 1133.1]}, {"text": "(“PowerAdvocate”), a provider of market, cost intelligence, and supply chain solutions serving the energy sector,", "bbox": [162.5, 1137.2, 1108.3, 1158.1]}, {"text": "for a net cash purchase price of $200.4 million, of which $10.0 million represents indemnity escrows. Within the", "bbox": [162.5, 1162.2, 1104.4, 1183.1]}, {"text": "Decision Analytics segment, PowerAdvocate expands the Company’s offerings to the energy sector by adding", "bbox": [162.5, 1187.2, 1083.7, 1208.1]}, {"text": "proprietary spend data and cost models and providing insight into customers’ cost savings opportunities. The", "bbox": [162.5, 1212.2, 1072.1, 1233.1]}, {"text": "preliminary purchase price allocation of the acquisition is presented in the table below.", "bbox": [162.5, 1237.2, 887.9, 1258.1]}, {"text": "On December 22, 2017, the Company acquired 100 percent of the asset of Service Software, LLC.", "bbox": [225.0, 1284.1, 1047.0, 1304.9]}, {"text": "(“Service Software”), a provider of business management software for the construction industry, for a net cash", "bbox": [162.5, 1309.1, 1085.9, 1329.9]}, {"text": "purchase price of $6.8 million, of which $0.5 million represents indemnity escrows. Within the Decision", "bbox": [162.5, 1334.1, 1035.4, 1354.9]}, {"text": "Analytics segment, Service Software expands the Company’s offerings to the insurance sector by integrating", "bbox": [162.5, 1359.1, 1071.1, 1379.9]}, {"text": "with the existing loss quantification solutions, which makes it possible for restoration professionals to save time", "bbox": [162.5, 1384.1, 1097.3, 1404.9]}, {"text": "by sharing job information, reducing duplicate data entry, and increasing productivity. The preliminary purchase", "bbox": [162.5, 1409.1, 1102.7, 1429.9]}, {"text": "price allocation of the acquisition is presented as part of “Others” in the table below.", "bbox": [162.5, 1434.1, 868.1, 1454.9]}, {"text": "81", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}